---
// Fundations
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<section class="bg-[#111110]">
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-24">
    <div
      class="max-w-prose"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="2000"
    >
      <p class="font-sans font-light text-lg leading-relaxed text-base-400">
        Most early-stage companies reach us the same way: they know something in their product or operations isn't working. They've got a specific request — a dashboard, a redesign, a new feature — and they're looking for someone to build it.
      </p>

      <p class="font-display text-2xl leading-snug text-[#f0ede8] my-12">
        We never just build the thing they asked for.
      </p>

      <p class="font-sans font-light text-lg leading-relaxed text-base-400 mb-10">
        Before we touch anything, we step back and look at the whole: the business model, the product architecture, the workflows, the data. Because nine times out of ten, the specific request is a symptom — and the actual opportunity is somewhere else.
      </p>

      <p class="font-sans font-light text-lg leading-relaxed text-base-400">
        That's the work. Finding where design and AI create real leverage for your business, sequencing the right moves, and executing with the speed and quality your investors and customers will notice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Wrapper>
</section>
